Armed Touch Casting					CATEGORY:FEAT			TYPE:General				PREMULT:3,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Casting],[PRESKILL:1,Spellcraft=9],[PREATT:6]				DESC:You deliver touch spells using a melee weapon.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.3			BENEFIT:When casting a spell with a range of touch, you may deliver the spell using a melee weapon or unarmed attack as a free action during the same turn. Though there is only one attack roll, the spell does not share the weapon’s critical range or multiplier. Instead, the spell uses the standard profile (critical range 20, ×2 damage). If both spell and weapon threaten a critical, roll each confirmation separately.
Battlecaster						CATEGORY:FEAT			TYPE:General				PREMULT:2,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Casting],[PREATT:6]										DESC:You can cast a spell as part of a full attack.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.3			BENEFIT:As a full attack action, after making your first attack, you may cast a spell with a casting time of a standard action or less instead of taking any additional attacks. If the spell results in an attack roll, that roll suffers a -5 penalty to hit.
