Potent Divination					CATEGORY:FEAT			TYPE:General				PRETEXT:Ability to cast a detection spell																DESC:Your detection spells are faster and stronger than normal.																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.7			BENEFIT:When you cast a detection spell (any spell beginning with the word detect), you learn in 1 round what you would normally learn in 3 rounds, the range extends to 120 ft., and the area extends 180 degrees in the direction you are facing.
